LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorA.label: Fuel Oil Generator A (building)
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorA.description: P : 12000W A rustic version of the standard UN Fuel Oil generator FGEN12K. Good production rate. Fuel Oil power generation with this engine is 15% more efficient than Chemfuel. Highly explosive if damaged.
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorB.label: Fuel Oil Generator B (building)
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorB.description: P : 12000W The industrial version of the UN Fuel Oil generator FGEN12K. Double injection system, double filtration system, High production rate. Fuel Oil power generation with this engine is 20% more efficient than Chemfuel. Highly explosive if damaged.
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorD.label: Fuel Oil Generator D (building)
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorD.description: P : 2250W A rustic and simple fuel oil generator, using a reliable combustion engine coupled with an alternator to generate electricity. Fuel Oil power generation with this engine is 10% more efficient than Chemfuel. Highly explosive if damaged.
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorF.label: Armored Generator F (building)
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorF.description: P : 2250W An industrial Diesel generator, using a reliable combustion engine coupled with an alternator to generate electricity. Very good production rate. Diesel power generation with this engine is 35% more efficient than Chemfuel. Highly explosive if damaged.
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorG.label: Armored Generator G (building)
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorG.description: P : 6000W An industrial Diesel generator, using a reliable combustion engine coupled with an alternator to generate electricity. Very good production rate. Diesel power generation with this engine is 40% more efficient than Chemfuel. Highly explosive if damaged.
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorM.label: Armored Generator M (building)
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorM.description: P : 6000W Military 6kW armored Diesel generator. UNSC standard, foolproof design, high production rate. Diesel power generation with this engine is 40% more efficient than Chemfuel. Highly explosive if damaged.
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorN.label: Armored Generator N (building)
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorN.description: P : 3000W Military 3kW armored Diesel generator. UNSC standard, foolproof design, high production rate. Diesel power generation with this engine is 40% more efficient than Chemfuel. Highly explosive if damaged.
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorV.label: Portable Generator V (building)
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorV.description: P : 750W A Diesel portable generator. Low capacity tank, low power but sufficient for most nomadic situations. Diesel power generation with this engine is 10% more efficient than Chemfuel.
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorW.label: Portable Generator W (building)
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorW.description: P : 750W A military Diesel generator. UNSC standard, low capacity but portable, foolproof design, high production rate. Diesel power generation with this engine is 10% more efficient than Chemfuel.
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorX.label: Portable Fuel Cell X (building)
LanguageData.Frame_SadjuukGeneratorX.description: P : 800W A Portable Fuel Cell that converts the chemical energy into electricity through an electrochemical reaction of hydrogen fuel with oxygen. Hydrogen Fuel cell power generation is 67% more efficient than Chemfuel.
